Vivian Health, Inc. Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 3/3/25
Thank you for joining the largest jobs portal for healthcare professionals. In this Privacy Policy, Vivian Health Inc. (“Vivian” or “we”) describes the types of personal information we collect when you visit and use the vivian.com website, app and associated services (the Vivian platform). We also describe how and why we use and share your personal information, how you can access and update your personal information and exercise your other legal rights as a user. Our services offered are not intended for anyone under the age of 18 or for anyone outside of the United States, and our personal information collection and use policies are designed accordingly. We will indicate changes to this Privacy Policy by updating the Effective Date above. If you continue to use the Vivian platform after the Effective Date of this Privacy Policy has changed, then the most up to date Privacy Policy will apply. A newly posted Privacy Policy with an updated Effective Date supersedes all previous Privacy Policies.
