hello@vivian.com
or write to us at 100 Pine Street, Suite 1250, PMB A140, San Francisco, CA 94111.
How to Opt Out of Selling, Sharing and Targeted Advertising (CA and VA)
To opt out of Sharing or Selling your Personal Information (if you are a California resident) or Targeted Advertising (if you are a Virginia resident), click on the “Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information” link in the footer of our website or click the link below.
Opt-out of Selling or Sharing for Targeted Advertising
This function is not activated if you do not have a California or Virginia IP address. If the button is not active, please try again from a California or Virginia location.
If you click on the above button to opt out of Selling or Sharing by Vivian for Targeted Advertising, Vivian will not allow our advertising partners to place new cookies or recognize any existing cookies they may have previously placed on your browser or device. The only Sales and Sharing for targeted Advertising we engage in is via cookies or tracking technologies.
Security of Your Personal Information
Vivian takes appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your personal information.We have different security measures based on the type and sensitivity of the personal information we collect and store. Vivian however cannot guarantee that all personal information we store and all communications between you and others via the Vivian.com platform will never be accessed by an unauthorized person.
The login credentials of your account, specifically your account password, is an important part of our security system, and it is your responsibility to protect it. You should not disclose your password to anyone, and if you believe your password or account has been compromised, you should change it immediately and contact us at
hello@vivian.com
to let us know.
Information Relating to Children
We do not knowingly collect information from children under the age of 16 years old (or older if required in an applicable jurisdiction to comply with applicable laws). If you are not over 16 years old (or older if required in an applicable jurisdiction to comply with applicable laws) then
DO NOT ACCESS OR USE THE SITE
. If you believe that we may have personal information from or about a child under the age of 16 years old, please contact us
here
Note that we'll attempt to delete the account of any child under the age of 16 that's reported to us as soon as possible. You are responsible for any and all account activity conducted by a minor on your account.
